OL,6,FDan Cordey, prosecuting, said Isak
OL,7,Fleft his home between 4pm and 10pm on
OL,8,FApril 4, and he discovered the break-
OL,9,Fin when he returned and saw his bins
OL,10,Fhad been moved.
OL,12,FThe gang broke into his TV room and
OL,13,F"inside an untidy search took place",
OL,14,FMr Cordey said.
OL,16,FCash between #5,000 and #10,000 was
OL,17,Ftaken, along with jewellery worth
OL,18,Fabout #68,000 and his Audi car, which
OL,19,Fa member of the public later found
OL,20,Fabandoned, jurors were told.
